.Dt RPKI-CLIENT 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm rpki-client
.Nd verifies route announcements
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl v
.Ar tal ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility verifies all route announcements starting with a trust anchor.
It uses
.Xr rsync 1
to fetch certificates, manifests, and route announcements themselves.
Its arguments are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl v
Prints information about status.
.It Ar tal
A trust anchor locator (TAL) file.
